rows.label: tlk42340111_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Kisasa always training to become
famous as salvager of legend.

rows.label: tlk42340111_03_msg0003
rows.name:
But other day, Kisasa ask Mochichi
to rate salvager skills...

rows.label: tlk42340111_03_msg0004
rows.name:
And Mochichi say Kisasa is worse
than amateur rookie salvager!

rows.label: tlk42340111_03_msg0005
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Kisasa spend so much time training,
forget to ever do any salvaging!

rows.label: tlk42340111_03_msg0006
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]To becoming salvager of legend,
apparently Kisasa must do lots of
salvage and haul up much treasure.
